desc: Kinugawa turbo Systems are built with the best quality using tools and balancing machines made by SCHENCK in Germany, balancing and quality of parts is a must when creating a performance turbocharger. Please make sure a special Anti-Counterfeit stamp located on the top right hand corner of your balance report sheet.

layout.text: All Kinugawa Turbos are balanced using a SCHENCK balancing machine from Germany
